readme:
This is Test Package.
==================

A hubot script to show available hubot commands

Installation
-----------------

In hubot project repo, run:

`npm install hubot-echo-cho --save`

Then add **hubot-echo-cho** to your `external-scripts.json`:

```json
["hubot-echo-cho"]
```

Configuration
-----------------
